OL,3,CFour arrested after incidents
OL,4,Cinvolving men armed with knives
OL,6,FFour people have been arrested
OL,7,Ffollowing altercations in Dungannon.
OL,9,FA man was injured and a property
OL,10,Fdamaged in separate incidents in the
OL,11,FCo Tyrone town on Monday night.
OL,13,FPolice said they received a report of
OL,14,Fan altercation involving about 10 men
OL,15,Farmed with knives and bats at a
OL,16,Fproperty at around 7.45pm in the
OL,17,FKillyman Road area.
OL,19,F"The men smashed the windows and
OL,20,Fcaused damage to the front door of a
OL,21,Fproperty," a police spokesperson said.
OL,26,@{D@AOU}D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/6
