PN,41702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1784119705
OL,3,CFour arrested after incidents
OL,4,Cinvolving men armed with knives
OL,6,F"Officers attended and a 32-year-old
OL,7,Fman was arrested on suspicion of
OL,8,Fcriminal damage. Two other men, aged
OL,9,F32 and 35, were arrested on suspicion
OL,10,Fof assault occasioning actual bodily
OL,11,Fharm. They remain in police custody at
OL,12,Fthis time."
OL,14,FAt 11pm, police said officers came
OL,15,Facross a large group of males gathered
OL,16,Fin the Newell Road area.
OL,18,F"Further reports had also been
OL,19,Freceived of a number of males in the
OL,20,Farea carrying knives and bats," they
OL,21,Fsaid.
