CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1784119705
OL,3,CFour arrested after incidents
OL,4,Cinvolving men armed with knives
OL,6,F"One man had been assaulted and
OL,7,Fsustained cuts to his hands and face.
OL,8,FHe attended hospital for treatment for
OL,9,Fhis injuries.
OL,11,F"An 18-year old man was arrested on
OL,12,Fsuspicion of grievous bodily harm and
OL,13,Fpossession of an offensive weapon with
OL,14,Fintent to commit an indictable offence.
OL,16,F"He remains in police custody.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOU
