PN,41704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1784119705
OL,3,CFour arrested after incidents
OL,4,Cinvolving men armed with knives
OL,6,F"I am appealing to anyone who may have
OL,7,Fwitnessed either altercation, or with
OL,8,FCCTV or other footage that could
OL,9,Fassist with inquiries, to contact
OL,10,Fpolice using our witness appeal form
OL,11,Fat https://reporting.psni.police.uk/
OL,12,Fappeals quoting reference 1755 13/07/
OL,13,F26, or call us on 101."
OL,15,FDUP Fermanagh and South Tyrone MLA
OL,16,FDeborah Erskine said she was deeply
OL,17,Fconcerned by reports from residents.
OL,19,F"There is no place for violence,
OL,20,Fintimidation or criminality on the
OL,21,Fstreets of Dungannon," she said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@WO]{D@AOU}D@VO]
