PN,41705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1784119705
OL,3,CFour arrested after incidents
OL,4,Cinvolving men armed with knives
OL,6,F"Criminality is criminality,
OL,7,Fregardless of who is involved or which
OL,8,Fsection of the community they come
OL,9,Ffrom. It must be called out and
OL,10,Fcondemned consistently. There can be
OL,11,Fno selective condemnation when it
OL,12,Fcomes to lawlessness and public
OL,13,Fdisorder.
OL,15,F"The PSNI must act decisively to
OL,16,Faddress these reports, reassure local
OL,17,Fresidents and help alleviate growing
OL,18,Fcommunity tensions and concerns.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU
