OL,3,CFour arrested after incidents
OL,4,Cinvolving men armed with knives
OL,6,F"People have a right to feel safe in
OL,7,Ftheir own homes and neighbourhoods,
OL,8,Fand any allegations of violence or
OL,9,Fintimidation must be thoroughly
OL,10,Finvestigated."
